        <body>       
                <pb n="1"/>
            <p>CHARLES HOFFMAN&#44;<lb/>
                ATTORNEY AT LAW&#44;<lb/>			
                S. E. COR. FIFTH &#38; CHESTNUT STS.<lb/></p>
            <p>SUBJECT&#44;&#95;&#95;&#95;&#95;&#95;&#95;&#95;&#95;&#95;<lb/>
                PHILADELPHIA&#44;&#95;&#95;&#95;&#95;&#95;&#95;&#95;&#95;&#95;&#95;189<lb/></p>
            <p>July 15th 0<lb/></p>
            <p>Dear Doctor Morais&#58;<lb/></p>
            <p>The name of the woman in Vilno to whom Rabbi <del>Kl</del><lb/> Kleinberg is <sic>indebtedand</sic> who wrote to me about it&#44; is Yenta Rivka<lb/> Alexandrowitch<lb/> Very Truly Yours<lb/> Charles Hoffman<lb/></p>
                
                <pb n="2"/>
            <p>This agreement made<lb/> the 26th day of June 1890<lb/> between Eliezer Kleinberg<lb/> and Dr Sabato Morais<lb/></p>
            <p>Whereas the said Klein&#45;<lb/>berg is indebted to a large amount<lb/> to sundry parties in Vilno Russia<lb/> and is desirous of repaying the<lb/> same<lb/></p>
            <p>Now in consideration of<lb/> the premises and the sum of<lb/> one dollar to him in hand paid<lb/> by the said Morais the receipt<lb/> whereof is acknowledged the<lb/> said Kleinberg agrees to pay monthly<lb/> to the said Morais one&#45;fourth<lb/> part of all the salary which he<lb/> receives or shall receive as rabbi<lb/></p>
                
                <pb n="3"/>
            <p>the said Morais to hold the said<lb/> money in trust and transmit it<lb/> to a responsible party in Russia<lb/> to be distributed among the said<lb/> Kleinberg&#39;s creditors<lb/></p>
            <p>This agreement to continue<lb/> until all the said Kleinberg&#39;s<lb/> indebtedness is paid and this said<lb/> contract to go into effect on<lb/> the first day of July 1890.<lb/></p>
            <p>Witness our hands<lb/> and seals the day and year just<lb/> above mentioned<lb/>
                Casey Kleinberg &#40;seal&#41;<lb/>
                Witnessed by<lb/> Charles Hoffman<lb/></p>
                
                <pb n="4"/>
            <p>&#91;Hebrew&#93;<lb/></p>
            
            <pb n="5"/>
            <p>FROM<lb/>
                CHARLES HOFFMAN&#44;<lb/>
                <del>DREXEL BUILDING</del>&#44;<lb/>
                PHILADELPHIA.<lb/>
                &#91;Re&#93;turn if not delivered in FIVE DAYS.<lb/></p>
            <p>Rev. Dr. S. Morais<lb/>
                546 N. 5th St<lb/>
                Phila<lb/></p>
            </body>
